/*** New feature ***/

Use Case ID - Seek help.
Description - Actor clicks the 'Help' button on the top bar.
Primary actor - Manager.

Use Case ID - About.
Description - Opens a pop-up with details about the application version and license.
Primary actor - Manager.

Use Case ID - ViewLog.
Description - Opens a pop-up where we can see the details of the last synchronisation session. 
Primary actor - Manager.

Use Case ID - Recover.
Description - Recovers the last project the actor was working on.
Primary actor - Manager.

/*** New feature ***/
Use Case ID - Tutorial.
Description - Opens the user's default browser and goes to a url with a description of how the application works.
Primary actor - Manager.
